name: New Manila
description: A cyberpunk city based on New Manila, inspired by an actual location of the same name. Procedurally generated using Voronoi textures, noise textures, and JSPlacement with added holograms and traffic. Rendered in Blender Eevee. Featured OBJKT: #167935 "amalgamation_006" by @GrotesqueChiq. By Lucius Felimus: https://www.luciusfelimus.com/
